WEBVTT

00:00:28.366 --> 00:00:30.413
could also be our undoing.

00:00:31.266 --> 00:00:35.357
We knew that if we thought
of our technology

00:00:35.381 --> 00:00:38.635
as a means to ever more power,

00:00:38.659 --> 00:00:42.366
if it was just a power trip,
we'd eventually destroy ourselves.

00:00:42.390 --> 00:00:43.571
That's what happens

00:00:43.595 --> 00:00:46.382
when you're on a power trip
and nothing else.

00:00:47.509 --> 00:00:50.898
So the idealism

00:00:50.922 --> 00:00:55.731
of digital culture back then

00:00:55.755 --> 00:01:00.494
was all about starting with
that recognition of the possible darkness